				"description": "**User Registration/Sign Up API**\n\nThis endpoint creates a new user account in the system.\n\n**Endpoint Details:**\n- **Method**: POST\n- **URL**: `/api/users`\n- **Content-Type**: `application/json`\n\n**Required Fields:**\n- `name` (String) - User's full name\n- `email` (String) - Unique email address\n- `password` (String) - User's password\n\n**Optional Fields:**\n- `phone` (String) - Phone number\n- `occupation` (String) - User's occupation\n- `role` (String) - User role: `\"USER\"` or `\"OWNER\"` (defaults to `\"USER\"`)\n\n**Response:**\n- **Success (200)**: Returns the created user object\n- **Error (400/500)**: Returns error message if validation fails\n\n**Example Success Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n  \"email\": \"john.doe@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"phone\": \"+91-9876543210\",\n  \"occupation\": \"Software Engineer\",\n  \"role\": \"USER\",\n  \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-15T10:30:00\",\n  \"updatedAt\": \"2024-01-15T10:30:00\"\n}\n```\n\n**Example Error Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Email already exists\"\n}\n```"
